#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.18"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.18:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.18:0.2"
msgid "2. Caravagga"
msgstr "2. Walking"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: nāgatisuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.18:0.3"
msgid "18. Dutiyaagatisutta"
msgstr "18. Prejudice (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.18:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, nāgatigamanāni."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, there are these four ways of making unprejudiced decisions."

msgctxt "an4.18:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.18:1.3"
msgid ""
"Na chandāgatiṃ gacchati, na dosāgatiṃ gacchati, na mohāgatiṃ gacchati, na "
"bhayāgatiṃ gacchati—"
msgstr ""
"Making decisions unprejudiced by favoritism, hostility, stupidity, and "
"cowardice."

msgctxt "an4.18:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri nāgatigamanānīti."
msgstr "These are the four ways of making unprejudiced decisions."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.18:2.1"
msgid "Chandā dosā bhayā mohā,"
msgstr "If you don’t act against the teaching"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.18:2.2"
msgid "yo dhammaṃ nātivattati;"
msgstr "out of favoritism, hostility, cowardice, and stupidity,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.18:2.3"
msgid "Āpūrati tassa yaso,"
msgstr "your fame swells,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.18:2.4"
msgid "sukkapakkheva candimā”ti."
msgstr "like the moon in the bright fortnight.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.18:2.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
